    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Moreover, Pandas only use one core of your operating system, which makes the process slow. In other words, we can say pandas do not support parallelism (breaking a problem into smaller tasks). Even if you can load a large data using pandas, a single operation will take many minutes to display the result, because of using a single core at a time.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
