        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Looping through numeric columns, finding the min and max values of each column, and using a simple mathematical formula to normalize those columns. It will be useless to display the numeric result using compute method until we perform all operations. It took only 0.1 seconds to perform a mathematical operation on this huge dataset!</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
