            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">We will be using the Scikit-learn library to demonstrate the purpose of dask-ml. Scikit-learn uses joblib because it helps in training most estimators using all the cores of your laptop. (Remember it only trains those models that contain the n_jobs parameter in it).</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
